description: Erection of a 36,552 sq.m tower and podium building 111.95 m AOD to provide 260 flats (158 studios, 75x1/23x2/4x3 bed), a 14,106 sq. m 169 bedroom hotel, a 605 sq. m health club, a 36 sq. m A1/A2/A3/B1 unit, 45 car parking spaces, landscaping and means of access. (Amendment of permitted development PA/03/1387).
